description.text:
After teaching for three years now I have noticed that there are two questions that are asked almost everyday:  
&quot;What is today's date?&quot;  
&quot;Can I borrow a pencil?&quot;  
Well the teacher desk companion now takes care of these questions along with answering some more uncommon questions.  
The teacher desk companion has calendar blocks, pencil/pen storage, USB drive holders, and a sticky note holder.   
All of these things are designed to make the day of a teacher a little bit easier!
